#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("This is Captain Haddock of the GTC Crecy. The Stalwart is coordinating with Command, so you're stuck with me.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("We've been poking around this graveyard for 72 hours. No survivors. Whatever hit the Riviera didn't leave anything for us to save.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("Our orders are to hold position until the science teams finish their analysis. I know you're bored, pilots. But trust me... boring is good. Boring keeps you alive.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


